# Error Handling

The application implements a comprehensive error handling system:

## Form Validation
- Client-side validation before submission
- Checks for required fields (title, meta description, target keyword, content)
- Displays validation errors in an error container

## API Error Handling
- Response status code checking
- JSON parsing of error responses
- Special handling for validation errors (422)
- Specific handling for API key errors

## UI Error Display
- Error container shows formatted error messages
- Bootstrap alert component with appropriate icons
- Error scrolling to ensure visibility
- Detailed error information when available from server

## Recovery
- Button state restoration after errors
- Clear error messages between operations
- Graceful degradation when services are unavailable
